Time-Left

Simple object model for time limits.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Time::Left

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        https://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Time-Left

    CPAN Ratings
        https://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Time-Left

    Search CPAN
        https://metacpan.org/release/Time-Left


